Package com.pushtechnology.diffusion.transform.updater

Package containing utilities for working with updaters.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BoundSafeUpdaterBuilder<S,T>
    An extension to SafeUpdaterBuilder that is bound to a session.
    BoundTransformedUpdaterBuilder<S,T>
    An extension to TransformedUpdaterBuilder that is bound to a session.
    BoundUpdaterBuilder<S,T,U extends TransformedUpdater<S,T>,V extends TransformedUpdateSource<S,T,U>>
    An extension to UpdaterBuilder that is bound to a session.
    SafeTransformedUpdater<S,T>
    An extension to TransformedUpdater that does not throw TransformationExceptions.
    SafeTransformedUpdateSource<S,T>
    An extension to TransformedUpdateSource that provides a SafeTransformedUpdater.
    SafeUpdaterBuilder<S,T>
    An extension to UpdaterBuilder that creates SafeTransformedUpdaters.
    TransformedUpdater<S,T>
    A value updater that transforms values to a type known to Diffusion.
    TransformedUpdaterBuilder<S,T>
    An extension to UpdaterBuilder that creates TransformedUpdaters.
    TransformedUpdateSource<S,T,U extends TransformedUpdater<S,T>>
    An update source for transformed values.
    UnboundSafeUpdaterBuilder<S,T>
    An extension to SafeUpdaterBuilder that is not bound to a session.
    UnboundTransformedUpdaterBuilder<S,T>
    An extension to TransformedUpdaterBuilder that is not bound to a session.
    UnboundUpdaterBuilder<S,T,U extends TransformedUpdater<S,T>,V extends TransformedUpdateSource<S,T,U>>
    An extension to UpdaterBuilder that is not bound to a session.
    UpdaterBuilder<S,T>
    Builder for TransformedUpdaters.
    ValueCache<S>
    Accessed to cached values.
